&quot;What percent rez you have&quot;<br>
<br>
I tell this person 90% but not rezzing right now about to enter a LDoN dungeon.  <br>
<br>
This person then ask what my loc is so they can bring the corpse to me.  I repeat that I am not rezzing about to enter the dungeon.  <br>
<br>
At that point he/she informs me that they are season 65 and need a rez and again asked for my loc.  Not sure what their season had to do with it but again told them sorry but can't rez. <br>
<br>
This person continued to send me tells even after I entered the dungeon, stating how awful I was for not rezzing them.<br>
<br>
I am not here to drop everything to go rez folks.  Yes if I can I do but when I say sorry I can't I mean sorry I can't.  <br>
<br>
Just needed to blow off a little steam.<br>
